data.description: Located in Hawthorne Ridge, 783 Stoneroot Drive offers a layout perfect for entertaining. The entryway is welcoming as you enter into the two story foyer with a formal dining room and separate living area to the right. The kitchen is spacious with a pantry, tons of cabinet storage and an eat in area. The family room is located off of the kitchen and extends into an additional flex space with double doors-perfect for an office or an additional bedroom as it has access to the full hall bath. Upstairs, you will find the owners suite with a separate sitting area and private bath including dual vanities, separate shower and tub, and a huge walk-in closet. Bedrooms 2, 3, and 4 all with walk in closets share the full hall bath upstairs. Outside, the owners have added a screened in porch which overlooks the fenced in backyard. Zoned for Blythewood Schools. Close to I-77 and a short commute to Downtown Columbia.
